thread.title_full: Introducing the enemies of the American people: George Rodrigue

author: George Rodrigue, The Plain Dealer
title: Introducing the enemies of the American people: George Rodrigue
text: President Trump's tweet calling journalists 'enemies of the people' raises the question of who those enemies are. A trip to the memorial wall at the Newseum, just down the street from the White House, offers thousands of answers.
